#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:1
msgid "Implicit Widget Representations Improvements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:3
msgid "VTK has better support for several vtkWidgetRepresentation subclasses."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:5
msgid "Bug fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:7
msgid ""
"Interactions are smoother thanks to a better Picker choice. Also, "
"interactively modifying radius (for Annulus, Cone and Cylinder) used to be "
"based on screen motion. Switching to mouse world position makes it more "
"intuitive: circle effectively follow the mouse cursor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:12
msgid "New BoundedWidget design"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:14
msgid ""
"vtkBoundedWidgetRepresentation is a new vtkWidgetRepresentation subclass, to "
"inherits from to benefit of a \"crop at outline\" feature. This is useful "
"for most vtkImplicitFunction representations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:18
msgid "API breaking changes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:20
msgid ""
"The classes that were ported to the vtkBoundedWidgetRepresentation design "
"loose some protected member, as the new parent class has same member as "
"`private`. Please use the Getters instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/widget-representations-improvements.md:24
msgid ""
"Concerned classes:  vtkImplicitConeRepresentation, "
"vtkImplicitCylinderRepresentation, vtkImplicitAnnulusRepresentation and "
"vtkImplicitPlaneRepresentation"
msgstr ""
